Package: ludisviz
Type: Package
Title: A package for visualizing stats on the Ludis Platform
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("OBH", "", email = "obh@ludisanalytics.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Ludis Analytics", role = "cph"))
Description: This package enables users to create basic data visualizations of match-level and season-level stats. It provides two types of functions:
    1) Functions that manipulate dataframes of stats to format them for data visualization (see format_data.R).
    2) Functions that create ggplot object visualizations using the formatted data frames (see visualize_data.R). These visualizations are optimized to be viewed using the plotly::ggplotly() function, which converts them to interactive plotly objects.
